"""Test move_volumes_between_storage_groups string parameter."""
payload = {'editStorageGroupActionParam': {'moveVolumeToStorageGroupParam':
    {'volumeId': [self.data.device_id], 'storageGroupId': self.data.
    storagegroup_name_1, 'force': 'false'}}}
with mock.patch.object(self.provisioning, 'modify_storage_group') as mock_mod:
    self.provisioning.move_volumes_between_storage_groups(self.data.
        device_id, self.data.storagegroup_name, self.data.storagegroup_name_1)
    mock_mod.assert_called_once_with(self.data.storagegroup_name, payload)
